{
  "stem": "365.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The following night, I could hardly move.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He says, come back tomorrow night.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How you feel?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So my friends took me down again to the infirmary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He took my temperature, and he just whistled.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He says, you are staying tomorrow in camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That tomorrow became almost three weeks.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "For two weeks, I was in a coma.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember, even, episodes from the high fever where I got up, put on my pants, and took my knapsack that I had, which you carried always and your pot for the soup.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the orderly there, what the hell is wrong with you?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Where are you going?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I said, I'm going home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He says, you idiot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You have a fever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You don't know what you're doing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Where-- where has a dog a home?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He says to me.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You have no home.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "That's your home.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And just threw me back on the rotten straw where we were laying, you know.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I remember like they were pulling down the-- one died next to me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So they just grabbed him by the legs, pulled him off.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And a new one came in.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Then from other side, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So I was thinking like in a dream.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "I says, when are they going to pull me off by the legs?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Anyways, I regained consciousness.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And with consciousness comes hunger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The hunger after typhus fever is just indescribable.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have seen people go literally mad from hunger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I received my ration of bread.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I tried to bite into it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I cannot bite bit into it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Every tooth in my jaws is loose.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I am just a skeleton, skin and bone.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Even the eyes have a wild look in them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The hair was, already after three weeks, a little bit grown, standing up like on a porcupine.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
